--- Rogelio Palomera <rpalomera(-at-)comcast.net> wrote:
>Well,
>
>It weird sound was indeed a loose valve. You guys are good!
>One of the valve adjusting screws was resting on the valve cover and was 
>stripped.
>I had to ride my bike 40mi to get a replacement screw, since none of the 
>FLAPS had
>one and I didn't want to wait for mail order (I will order a couple though 
>next time I place
>an order)... Put the new screw in and readjusted the valves. The engine now 
>sounds better,
>I think, although I suspect an exhaust leak. Sound bite can be heard at
>
>http://rpalomera.home.comcast.net/VW/
>
>or directly at http://home.comcast.net/~rpalomera/VW/VW106.wav
